Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Coppelia之柩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.13,0:00:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,流下的淚水早已乾枯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,對血感到飢渴的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡散發著\N{\fs8}\N{\r}天使柔和羽毛氣息飛舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗太陽不西沉的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,任誰都沉默不語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,彷彿奇術般的運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,見不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.50,0:00:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡見不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,能夠拯救我們的神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Coppelia之柩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:01:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,人們是疲疲的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,祭壇的羔羊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,機械夢想究竟朝向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Coppelia之柩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,從黑暗甦醒的光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,祭壇的羔羊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,螺絲中斷的夢想究竟朝向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Noir
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.72,0:01:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,其乃自古命運之名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.09,0:01:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,掌管死亡的兩名少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗聖手為幼嬰帶來安詳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我是法尼爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我這邊得到一些情報
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,對﹐就是上次那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不﹐詳細等見了面再告訴妳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,明天下午來我家好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我老婆也想見妳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我們來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:05.27,Title,,0,0,0,,#05 索達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我害的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在調查\N{\fs8}\N{\r}最近跟碟克斯接觸過的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我也請法尼爾幫我找情報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,然後他被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,連家人也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,再想下去也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他們打算將我們…將Noir消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我們當初會見面只是偶然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是誰叫妳來殺Noir的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是妳妳會說出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,妳叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,妳問這個幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不論是妳或我都不會有\N{\fs8}\N{\r}能刻上名字的墳墓…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,法尼爾一定抓到了他們的把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,幫花澆水是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不過﹐那些花\N{\fs8}\N{\r}可能很快就會被染成黑色喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Noir…我也聽過這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,它是這個行業最老的稱號之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但是沒有人知道它的由來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這個拼圖盡是些\N{\fs8}\N{\r}來路不明的圖塊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,名為Noir的圖塊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,妳這個圖塊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,以及另外一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我去問看看法尼爾的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,妳不用來沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真是殘忍\N{\fs8}\N{\r}居然全家都被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,法尼爾是個很講義氣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,即使當上了老大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒忘記提拔曾當過他大哥的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他很有老大風範\N{\fs8}\N{\r}但也是個很顧家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他可是很疼愛他的妻女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他老婆為人又很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那對夫妻是少數能信賴的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,對了﹐妳剛才問我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,關於上禮拜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯﹐就是上禮拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就如妳所說的﹐他的確來過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因為兩年沒見到他了\N{\fs8}\N{\r}所以我的印象格外深刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他有說什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,沒說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細想想﹐他的臉色似乎不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,對了﹐他用妳的名字\N{\fs8}\N{\r}開了一瓶酒放在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那瓶酒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他說下次想跟妳喝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,敬山坎教會的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼是山坎教會的回憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我從沒去過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,d跟5畫圓圈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,g跟7畫三角形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,法尼爾似乎是找到了\N{\fs8}\N{\r}很大一條線索
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因此感到害怕而把它藏了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,大概就藏在山坎教會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,山坎教會有的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,禮拜堂和鍾樓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,修道院、僧侶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,藥草園
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,墓窟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,d…droite\N{\fs8}\N{\r}（droite為法文“右邊”）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,右5
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,右5
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,g是gauche\N{\fs8}\N{\r}（gauche為法文“左邊”）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,左7
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,3
